/>\n大家本來都有傾開，加上同班都多機會接觸，佢平日就比較毒都係睇下動漫嗰類人，對於近期啲電影我又無乜了解所以唔知點選擇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9585cf99fc8a4ed8944f79d591cf0dfa8de225f","tid":430930,"uid":106598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T18:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一撚定係睇鬼片，挨下挨下一野拖住佢隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前有試過同一班人一齊去睇鬼片，佢嘅反應都係勁驚，我怕佢會嚇到有啲反感<br />\n<br />\nBtw近期有咩鬼故好推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71acf22cd3a61eb5554183f9ac7a1d2254035866","tid":430930,"uid":106598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T18:06:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>約到先諗睇咩戲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n約到嘅時候巴打記得幫幫手諗下有咩好提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a221677dd01c7a28105b12bf37c5a9a9ba13fd1b","tid":430930,"uid":22347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T18:08:47.000Z","msg":"可以去睇解憂雜貨店"},{"pid":"4ff45c1fe7a40cd822d4a9903a33ef9774f8055f","tid":430930,"uid":106598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T18:12:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以去睇解憂雜貨店</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打嘅建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我去做下功課睇下講咩先"}]}